549
00:52:06,180 --> 00:52:11,540
But even then, Dr. Oh followed her conscience as a doctor and chose the patient.

550
00:52:12,680 --> 00:52:15,000
I learned a lot this time from Dr. Oh.

551
00:52:15,000 --> 00:52:17,540
So please just forgive her now.

552
00:52:17,540 --> 00:52:20,000
Please do me a favor.

553
00:52:21,500 --> 00:52:24,040
<i>There's nothing to forgive.<i></i></i>

