00:52:25,930 --> 00:52:28,000
Sit down, sit down.

555
00:52:28,910 --> 00:52:31,250
Sit down.

556
00:52:31,250 --> 00:52:33,700
Here...

557
00:52:33,700 --> 00:52:36,540
Welcome back.

558
00:52:52,510 --> 00:52:55,450
