00:54:21,760 --> 00:54:25,160
That most likely he will never come back again.

577
00:54:25,160 --> 00:54:29,060
The seal of the memory broke...

578
00:54:29,060 --> 00:54:31,410
Do you have a gist of what that means?

579
00:54:31,410 --> 00:54:33,970
I really don't know.

